<plot>Aging composer 'Franz Liszt' (qv) lives in an abbey. On his birthday, a priest brings him a box that was just delivered to the abbey. There is no return address. In the box he finds a single flower. The flower brings back memories of his lost love of long ago, who inspired him to compose his unforgettable melodies.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?009908</url></doc>
